data.description: *Price Improvement.* Don't Miss this Opportunity. Welcome to 63453 Walpi Dr. Discover serenity at this Joshua Tree residence, situated on paved roads and nearly half an acre. 3-beds, 2-bath home with 1,752 sq.ft. of meticulously designed living space, accompanied by an attached 2-car garage. The main living area welcomes you with soaring 14 feet vaulted ceilings. Step into a recently remodeled kitchen that features updated cabinets & granite countertops. Every detail has been carefully considered. Upgraded LVP flooring throughout the home provides both durability and style. This home has a showcase of thoughtful upgrades. The primary bedroom features an en-suite bathroom and a custom closet system. Samsung appliances, including a smart front load washer and steam gas dryer add a touch of modern convenience to your daily routine. Enjoy the serene surroundings with beautiful mountain and desert views and the convenience of being just 10 minutes from downtown Joshua Tree, 15 minutes from Joshua Tree National Park and Yucca Valley, and a short 25-minute drive to Pioneer Town. For those connected to the 29 Palms MCAGCC Base, you'll find yourself only 30 minutes away.
